[{"id":"VR852785","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">What is the direction of the momentum of the piece having mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3 m\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"3 m\" overflow=\"scroll\"> <mn>3</mn> <mi>m</mi> </math></span></span> immediately after the explosion?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR852785_rubric","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<div>\n<div class=\"stimulus_reference\">\n<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A stationary block explodes, breaking into three pieces of masses <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"m\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>m</mi></math></span></span>, <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"m\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>m</mi></math></span></span>, and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"3 m\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"3 m\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>3</mn><mi>m</mi></math></span></span>. The two pieces of mass <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"m\" overflow=\"scroll\"> <mi>m</mi> </math></span></span> move off at right angles to each other with the same magnitudes of momentum <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"m v\" role=\"math\"><math alttext=\"m v\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mi>m</mi><mi>v</mi></mstyle></math></span></span>, as shown in the figure.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows two momentum vectors, each of magnitude m v, at a 90 degree angle. One vector points horizontally to the left, and the other vector points vertically downward.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR852785.g01.svg\" /></div>\n"}],"choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"inline_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows an arrow pointing diagonally upward and to the right.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR852785.g03.svg\"></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"inline_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows an arrow pointing diagonally downward and to the left.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR852785.g05.svg\"></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"inline_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows an arrow pointing vertically upward.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR852785.g07.svg\"></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"inline_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows an arrow pointing horizontally to the right.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR852785.g09.svg\"></span></p>"],"answer":0}]